metadata.name: FAKERAREHEADLINES - The Memes 03/Jan/2009 Chancellor brings bitcoin backing to banks #1/69
metadata.description:
"The Memes 03/Jan/2009 Chancellor brings bitcoin backing to banks" will now be forever etched on-chain. The copy was generated using GPT3 prompted on the headlines and edited to fit the space. 

Anyone can make their own FAKERAREHEADLINES, and the audience is invited to imagine what the news would look like in this parallel universe, and write their headlines on-chain either by signing a message or else by etching their message on this NFT using ETCH by Deca x Matt Kane.
